声明！
This is an unofficial translation of the The MIT License into simplified Chinese. It was not published by the MIT, and does not legally state the distribution terms for software that uses the original MIT English text does that. However, we hope that this translation will help Chinese speakers understand the MIT License.
这是一份MIT的非官方中文简体翻译。它并非MIT发布，也不是使用MIT授权的软件的法定发布条款——只有MIT授权的英文原版具有这样的效力。然而，我们希望这份翻译能够帮助中文读者更好的理解MIT授权。
